                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <h4 class="mb-0"><a href="#" class="text-3 text-uppercase font-weight-bold pt-2 d-block text-dark text-decoration-none">Project server integration in minutes, not weeks!</a></h4>
                        <p class="text-2">The Project Integration Engine (PIE for short) makes it easy to integrate other systems data into Project Server. Create Projects, Tasks, Resources, Assignments (and more) and keep them in sync with your other systems</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
